WEIGHTRANK1="normal weight."
WEIGHTRANK2="fat."
WEIGHTRANK3="overweight."
WEIGHTRANK4="obese."
WEIGHTRANK5="morbidly obese."
WEIGHTRANK6="very severely obese."
WEIGHTRANK7="extremely heavily severely morbidly obese."
